<p>Hello <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password associated with your account.</p>

<p>
  To reset your password, please click the button below:
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to 'Reset My Password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "display:inline-block; padding:10px 20px; background-color:#28a745; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:5px;" %>
</p>

<p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your current password will remain unchanged.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The <%= Rails.application.class.module_parent_name %> Team</p>
